## Setup & Installation

### Requirements

- [Homebrew](https://brew.sh) and [go-task](https://taskfile.dev)
[% if use_node %]
- Node >= 22 and [pnpm](https://pnpm.io)
[% endif %]
[% if use_python %]
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) (Python is pinned in `.python-version`)
[% endif %]

### Install

```bash
task bootstrap   # one-time machine setup (Homebrew[% if use_node %] + Node + pnpm[% endif %])
task install     # Brewfile deps[% if use_python %] + uv sync[% endif %][% if use_node %] + pnpm install[% endif %] + lefthook git hooks
task verify      # confirm everything passes
```

Or open the repo in the devcontainer (VS Code "Reopen in Container", or a
[Coder](https://coder.com) workspace)[% if devcontainer %] — the human profile lives in
`.devcontainer/dev/`, the AI/bot profile at `.devcontainer/`[% endif %].

New here? Start with [docs/onboarding.md](docs/onboarding.md) and the
post-generation [docs/CHECKLIST.md](docs/CHECKLIST.md).

